Chef/Owner Chris Fennell
Northwest Grille has been family-owned and operated since we opened the doors in 1996! We treat every customer like they are a part of our family. We strive to serve food that is locally produced and of the finest quality at a great value. In 2011, Chef Chris Fennell became the sole owner of the restaurant he helped establish. Visit Northwest Grille and re-discover what makes our restaurant a special part of the Gainesville community.
